flowchart LR
  subgraph intent["Recovered Segment 5A design"]
    A0["S0 Gate and seal<br/>Verifies Layer-1 PASS authority<br/>and freezes the Layer-2 input world"]
    A1["S1 Demand-class and base-scale authority<br/>Classifies merchant-zone demand persona<br/>and weekly scale"]
    A2["S2 Weekly shape authority<br/>Builds deterministic unit-mass local-week<br/>shape templates"]
    A3["S3 Baseline intensity composition<br/>Turns scale plus shape into baseline<br/>merchant-zone weekly intensity truth"]
    A4["S4 Calendar and scenario overlays<br/>Projects baseline into horizon-level<br/>scenario intensity truth"]
    A5["S5 Validation and final gate<br/>Audits S0 through S4 and seals<br/>consumer legitimacy"]
