  A0 --> A1 --> A2 --> A3 --> A4 --> A5

  B0["Actual design shifts that matter"] --> B1["S0 became a real Layer-2 gate:<br/>it had to understand all Layer-1 bundle laws<br/>and define a strict S0-vs-S1+ fail-fast split"]
