  B0 --> B3["S2 stayed deterministic and template-driven,<br/>but the implemented design locked to a mixed-channel weekly-shape posture<br/>for the actual output world"]
  B0 --> B4["S3 became the main baseline-composition authority<br/>and later the tail-richness owner surface"]
  B0 --> B5["S4 became both overlay-governance authority and<br/>later a memory-safe execution boundary,<br/>which materially changed how the segment could be run"]
  B0 --> B6["S5 stayed the final validation rail:<br/>it signs the whole Layer-2 traffic world but does not tune it"]

